## CesiumJS Webpack Config (DO NOT MODIFY)
The `next.config.ts` contains a CopyWebpackPlugin that copies Cesium static assets. If you modify `next.config.ts`, preserve this block exactly:
```ts
new CopyWebpackPlugin({
  patterns: [
    { from: path.join(cesiumSource, 'Workers'),    to: 'static/Cesium/Workers' },
    { from: path.join(cesiumSource, 'ThirdParty'), to: 'static/Cesium/ThirdParty' },
    { from: path.join(cesiumSource, 'Assets'),     to: 'static/Cesium/Assets' },
    { from: path.join(cesiumSource, 'Widgets'),    to: 'static/Cesium/Widgets' },
  ],
})
config.resolve.alias['cesium'] = path.resolve(__dirname, cesiumSource)
config.module.unknownContextCritical = false
```
